- cs.TL (Temporal Logic) is a possibility because the paper deals with infinite streams of discrete values, which can be seen as a temporal sequence of events. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possibility because the paper discusses the use of trees as representations of functions.
